5dd51998-264a-405e-88a7-dc5e071d1b43.do_description: To make the output, you have to...draw the shapes in dark blue to fill the empty black squares at the top, then color the gray squares black.
5dd51998-264a-405e-88a7-dc5e071d1b43.see_description: In the input, you should see...gray shapes at the bottom edge corresponding with empty space in the field at the top.

7e9cb293-209b-45a9-9153-813288ba9754.do_description: To make the output, you have to... the item fill the ground like piece from a well-know game, and the item become dark blue.
7e9cb293-209b-45a9-9153-813288ba9754.grid_description: The output grid size... is the same as the input grid.
7e9cb293-209b-45a9-9153-813288ba9754.see_description: In the input, you should see... a red "ground" at the top of the grid and some gray item below.
